with your friends,

335
00:13:54,144 --> 00:13:56,379
but I want to meet
this girl first.

336
00:13:57,512 --> 00:13:59,112
That's very reasonable.

337
00:13:59,181 --> 00:14:00,271
Thank you.

338
00:14:00,409 --> 00:14:01,747
You're welcome.

339
00:14:01,980 --> 00:14:04,049
Now, can you please reach
the dryer sheets?

340
