isn't helping right now.

387
00:16:03,314 --> 00:16:05,004
Right. Sorry.

388
00:16:05,434 --> 00:16:07,646
She is almost twice your age.

389
00:16:07,715 --> 00:16:09,708
There are people
five times my age

390
00:16:09,777 --> 00:16:11,388
