physical maturity,

404
00:16:40,801 --> 00:16:43,410
all things that have nothing
to do with being smart.

405
00:16:43,512 --> 00:16:46,168
Are you suggesting
I'm not emotionally mature?

406
00:16:46,262 --> 00:16:48,020
